Prepare pudding as directed on package except--use 1 3/4 cup milk. Refrigerate at least 1 hour. When ready to assemble parfaits, stir chai tea into pudding. In 4 wine glasses or glass dessert dishes, layer about 1/4 cup pudding, 1 tablespoon granola, 2 tablespoons whipped topping, about 1/4 cup additional pudding and remaining tablespoon granola for each parfait.